WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.380 --> 00:00:04.380
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

00:00:04.380 --> 00:00:07.830
<i>♪ ♪</i>

00:00:07.830 --> 00:00:11.000
<i>- What happened was,
he was on the plane,</i>

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:13.710
and he was served lunch,

00:00:13.710 --> 00:00:16.750
and on the plate was
some broccoli.

00:00:16.750 --> 00:00:19.210
<i>He sees the plate in front
of him, he sits back,</i>

00:00:19.210 --> 00:00:21.290
he looks at the steward,
and he says, "You know,

00:00:21.290 --> 00:00:24.290
<i>"I've hated broccoli ever
since I was a little boy.</i>

00:00:24.290 --> 00:00:26.210
<i>"My mother made me
eat broccoli.</i>

00:00:26.210 --> 00:00:28.170
<i>"And now that I'm President
of the United States,</i>

00:00:28.170 --> 00:00:29.920
<i>"I'm not gonna eat broccoli
anymore.</i>

00:00:29.920 --> 00:00:31.790
"I don't want to see it,
I don't want to smell it,

00:00:31.790 --> 00:00:33.040
"I don't want it around me.

00:00:33.040 --> 00:00:34.620
It's gone from this plane."

00:00:34.620 --> 00:00:36.000
So they banned broccoli
from Air Force One.

00:00:38.750 --> 00:00:40.670
<i>- One day, we were an hour out</i>

00:00:40.670 --> 00:00:43.460
<i>and the president's doctor
came up to me</i>

00:00:43.460 --> 00:00:45.250
extremely seriously and said,

00:00:45.250 --> 00:00:47.830
"Howie, was there broccoli
in that lasagna for lunch?"

00:00:47.830 --> 00:00:49.830
And I said, "Yes, sir,
there was."

00:00:49.830 --> 00:00:51.420
And he said, "Well, you know,

00:00:51.420 --> 00:00:53.330
the President's allergic
to broccoli."

00:00:53.330 --> 00:00:54.670
<i>♪ ♪</i>

00:00:54.670 --> 00:00:56.210
<i>That really hit me.</i>

00:00:56.210 --> 00:00:58.080
<i>I am supposed
to know that stuff.</i>

00:00:58.080 --> 00:00:59.880
<i>And I go downstairs,
and the doctor</i>

00:00:59.880 --> 00:01:01.880
<i>is now getting a shot</i>

00:01:01.880 --> 00:01:03.960
out of his bag to give
to the President.

00:01:03.960 --> 00:01:05.290
And I said, "How is he doing?"

00:01:05.290 --> 00:01:07.330
He said, "He's not doing well."

00:01:07.330 --> 00:01:10.880
<i>Two Secret Service gentlemen
are holding the President up</i>

00:01:10.880 --> 00:01:13.420
<i>on each side, and he's
kind of staggering</i>

00:01:13.420 --> 00:01:15.580
out to go down the steps.

00:01:15.580 --> 00:01:17.580
Now, this--
I'm feeling terrible.

00:01:17.580 --> 00:01:21.080
<i>My pager went off,
and my deputy said,</i>

00:01:21.080 --> 00:01:23.000
"Chief, the pilot
needs to see you

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:24.830
in the pilot's office."

00:01:24.830 --> 00:01:26.420
<i>You're walking into
the office,</i>

00:01:26.420 --> 00:01:27.880
<i>and the whole crew was
in the office,</i>

00:01:27.880 --> 00:01:29.330
<i>and I'm panicking.</i>

00:01:29.330 --> 00:01:30.830
And I looked over,
and Colonel Jackson,

00:01:30.830 --> 00:01:32.750
our navigator--fine fella--

00:01:32.750 --> 00:01:36.080
uh, I think he knew
I was really high-strung,

00:01:36.080 --> 00:01:38.500
and he gave me the thumbs-up
with a smile.

00:01:38.500 --> 00:01:41.750
And I said, "Oh, you guys
are messing with me."

00:01:41.750 --> 00:01:44.080
<i>They were all in on it,
the entire crew</i>

00:01:44.080 --> 00:01:46.920
and the President and his
staff and the doctor.

00:01:46.920 --> 00:01:48.790
<i>They were all in
on the prank.</i>

